00:29:54.318 --> 00:29:56.199
Just holding your hand, P'Charm,

00:29:56.672 --> 00:29:58.705
living a normal life together...

00:29:58.942 --> 00:30:00.974
this world is already beautiful enough.

00:30:09.100 --> 00:30:10.066
Hello, Mom and Dad.

00:30:10.200 --> 00:30:10.937
Hello.

00:30:10.937 --> 00:30:11.437
Hello.

00:30:11.600 --> 00:30:12.400
Hello.

00:30:13.100 --> 00:30:15.179
Charmie!

00:30:16.366 --> 00:30:18.333
Greeting the cat before your own mother?

00:30:18.666 --> 00:30:19.500
Greet me too.

00:30:20.300 --> 00:30:21.366
I missed you the most.

00:30:22.300 --> 00:30:23.566
I missed you too, sweetie.

00:30:24.333 --> 00:30:25.818
Mom,

00:30:25.818 --> 00:30:28.119
I was only gone for a week.

00:30:28.119 --> 00:30:31.333
I'll see you every day once I go back to work.

00:30:31.866 --> 00:30:33.382
Of course I missed you.

00:30:33.382 --> 00:30:34.166
I missed you too.

00:30:37.500 --> 00:30:38.420
By the way,

00:30:38.420 --> 00:30:41.789
you said Charmie looks like me.

00:30:42.404 --> 00:30:44.148
How so?

00:30:49.733 --> 00:30:52.333
Literally everywhere.

00:30:54.533 --> 00:30:55.333
What?

00:30:56.500 --> 00:30:58.133
I think I'm much cuter.

00:30:59.466 --> 00:31:01.800
And I don't have a chubby belly like this.

00:31:02.566 --> 00:31:04.166
Charmie doesn't have a chubby belly.

00:31:05.160 --> 00:31:06.232
Yes, he does.

00:31:08.752 --> 00:31:09.860
Mom, Dad...

00:31:10.191 --> 00:31:12.864
we should get going now.

00:31:13.000 --> 00:31:13.541
Oh?

00:31:13.920 --> 00:31:17.579
Aren't you staying for dinner, Ping, Charm?

00:31:18.300 --> 00:31:21.666
We're going to cook dinner tonight.

00:31:22.066 --> 00:31:22.866
Huh?

00:31:23.700 --> 00:31:25.333
Am I hearing things?

00:31:25.566 --> 00:31:27.333
You're cooking?

00:31:27.700 --> 00:31:28.500
Oh, Mom...

00:31:29.000 --> 00:31:29.800
Huh.

00:31:30.800 --> 00:31:31.866
Why, Mom?

00:31:32.400 --> 00:31:34.366
She told me she's going to cook for me.

00:31:34.966 --> 00:31:37.300
I thought she cooks all the time.

00:31:38.700 --> 00:31:42.212
Well, once you taste her cooking,

00:31:42.212 --> 00:31:44.500
let me know how it goes.

00:31:45.333 --> 00:31:46.133
Mom!

00:31:47.500 --> 00:31:48.733
See you later, kids.

00:31:49.066 --> 00:31:49.866
Okay.

00:31:50.466 --> 00:31:51.366
Love you, Mom and Dad.

00:31:51.600 --> 00:31:52.700
Love you too, dear.

00:31:53.066 --> 00:31:55.533
Come here, Charmie. I missed you so much.

00:31:56.500 --> 00:31:57.733
Charmie, don't be stubborn.

00:31:58.000 --> 00:31:58.785
Let's see...

00:31:58.785 --> 00:31:59.285
Here.

00:32:00.166 --> 00:32:01.266
Let Mommy take a picture of you.

00:32:06.519 --> 00:32:07.682
Charmie,

00:32:07.682 --> 00:32:08.476
look here, baby.

00:32:08.476 --> 00:32:09.213
Charm, look here.

00:32:09.213 --> 00:32:10.503
One, two...

00:32:10.503 --> 00:32:11.746
Hold the pose for Mommy.

00:32:11.983 --> 00:32:13.098
Okay, one...

00:32:13.382 --> 00:32:14.222
two...

00:32:50.600 --> 00:32:52.126
P'Charm...

00:32:52.457 --> 00:32:55.097
I'm trying my best here.

00:32:55.400 --> 00:32:56.713
Why is it taking so long?

00:32:57.376 --> 00:32:59.329
I'm waiting to eat.

00:32:59.966 --> 00:33:02.666
P'Charm, go sit and wait properly.

00:33:05.766 --> 00:33:06.800
Hurry up, behave.

00:33:07.366 --> 00:33:08.166
Mhmm.

00:33:08.400 --> 00:33:10.466
Hmm, stubborn?

00:33:11.333 --> 00:33:12.066
Take this!

00:33:12.066 --> 00:33:12.866
Come here!

00:33:13.266 --> 00:33:14.066
Spin.

00:33:14.500 --> 00:33:15.299
Go on.

00:33:15.299 --> 00:33:15.799
Mhmm.

00:33:15.866 --> 00:33:16.542
Spin.

00:33:16.542 --> 00:33:17.042
Mhmm.

00:33:17.042 --> 00:33:17.542
Walk.

00:33:20.266 --> 00:33:21.200
Sit nicely.

00:33:22.900 --> 00:33:23.700
Hup!

00:33:29.900 --> 00:33:31.081
P'Charm...

00:33:31.081 --> 00:33:32.066
I'm sorry.

00:33:33.133 --> 00:33:35.333
I didn't think it'd be this hard.

00:33:36.700 --> 00:33:39.066
You'll just have to eat an omelet today.

00:33:41.200 --> 00:33:42.869
Your omelet

00:33:43.579 --> 00:33:45.776
looks like the most delicious thing in the world.

00:33:49.400 --> 00:33:50.925
It's okay.

00:33:51.304 --> 00:33:53.979
I ordered some more food too.

00:33:57.200 --> 00:33:59.266
They're all your favorites.

00:34:03.100 --> 00:34:03.900
This too.

00:34:04.566 --> 00:34:05.366
Here.

00:34:09.300 --> 00:34:10.100
Thank you.

00:34:12.400 --> 00:34:14.800
Let me taste it.

00:34:21.866 --> 00:34:22.666
Mmm.

00:34:23.733 --> 00:34:24.533
It's so delicious.

00:34:26.533 --> 00:34:27.366
P'Charm...

00:34:28.500 --> 00:34:29.304
Heh.

00:34:29.304 --> 00:34:31.166
You don't have to lie to please me.

00:34:33.300 --> 00:34:34.666
I'm not lying.

00:34:35.500 --> 00:34:36.866
I really mean it.

00:34:38.300 --> 00:34:41.400
This omelet, you made with heart just for me.

00:34:45.733 --> 00:34:46.652
And...

00:34:47.646 --> 00:34:49.350
the chef is delicious too.

00:34:50.966 --> 00:34:51.776
P'Charm!

00:34:53.533 --> 00:34:54.333
Talking like that...

00:34:55.700 --> 00:34:57.900
should I make it for you every day?

00:34:59.900 --> 00:35:00.835
Uh...

00:35:01.166 --> 00:35:02.206
I think...

00:35:02.632 --> 00:35:03.993
maybe not.

00:35:03.993 --> 00:35:06.033
If you cook for me every day,

00:35:06.270 --> 00:35:08.879
I think I'll get fat.

00:35:11.766 --> 00:35:14.366
Are you tired?

00:35:15.000 --> 00:35:16.800
No, just a little bit.

00:35:22.400 --> 00:35:24.014
I'm so glad

00:35:24.392 --> 00:35:25.911
to have you here.

00:35:27.100 --> 00:35:29.133
Honestly, you don't have to do anything.

00:35:29.666 --> 00:35:31.400
Just having you by my side like this,

00:35:32.266 --> 00:35:34.466
I'm already the happiest person in the world.

00:35:36.123 --> 00:35:37.205
Then...

00:35:39.966 --> 00:35:41.566
should we go take a shower?

00:36:09.366 --> 00:36:10.700
Just relax.

00:36:12.300 --> 00:36:13.280
Tonight,

00:36:14.037 --> 00:36:16.690
I'll help you unwind.

00:36:23.466 --> 00:36:24.533
Do you know?

00:36:25.266 --> 00:36:26.066
You're beautiful,

00:36:27.500 --> 00:36:28.485
and...

00:36:29.195 --> 00:36:30.821
incredibly sexy too.

00:36:32.133 --> 00:36:33.933
I won't allow anyone else to see you like this.

00:36:34.700 --> 00:36:35.500
Only I get to see,

00:36:36.866 --> 00:36:38.766
only I get to do this to you.

00:36:40.733 --> 00:36:42.479
Who was it that said

00:36:43.378 --> 00:36:45.353
they didn't like showering with me?

00:36:46.016 --> 00:36:47.358
Then...

00:36:47.973 --> 00:36:49.678
maybe I should stop?

00:36:50.333 --> 00:36:51.516
No, don't stop.

00:36:51.942 --> 00:36:53.937
Let's keep showering.

00:37:03.166 --> 00:37:04.400
I love you.

00:37:06.400 --> 00:37:08.166
I love bathing you the most.

00:37:09.300 --> 00:37:10.600
Let's shower like this every day.

00:38:08.733 --> 00:38:09.934
P'Charm...

00:38:11.590 --> 00:38:13.292
Do you think...

00:38:14.617 --> 00:38:16.907
we'll love each other like this forever?

00:38:19.966 --> 00:38:21.200
I'm so scared.

00:38:25.933 --> 00:38:27.333
I don't know either.

00:38:28.966 --> 00:38:30.366
What the future holds.

00:38:33.300 --> 00:38:35.269
But I will make every day

00:38:36.074 --> 00:38:37.938
the best it can be.

00:38:38.900 --> 00:38:40.200
You don't have to be scared.

00:38:42.000 --> 00:38:44.066
No matter how many Valentines,

00:38:45.500 --> 00:38:46.300
how many months,

00:38:47.366 --> 00:38:48.166
how many years,

00:38:50.200 --> 00:38:51.566
I will always love you,

00:38:52.300 --> 00:38:53.566
love only you.

00:39:10.500 --> 00:39:11.454
Let me

00:39:13.300 --> 00:39:15.358
make you happy for a change, P'Charm?

00:40:56.733 --> 00:40:57.993
I never thought

00:40:59.366 --> 00:41:02.233
we'd be walking here together again

00:41:02.990 --> 00:41:04.032
like this.

00:41:07.600 --> 00:41:08.400
True.

00:41:11.533 --> 00:41:13.366
But looking back,

00:41:15.366 --> 00:41:17.500
I still feel guilty towards you.

00:41:18.933 --> 00:41:19.733
P'Charm.

00:41:20.566 --> 00:41:21.466
I'm sorry.

00:41:23.166 --> 00:41:25.866
How many times have you apologized?

00:41:29.400 --> 00:41:30.664
It's really okay.

00:41:31.753 --> 00:41:33.060
Honestly,

00:41:34.433 --> 00:41:35.989
if that hadn't happened that day,

00:41:37.503 --> 00:41:39.817
we probably wouldn't
be loving each other like this.

00:41:41.533 --> 00:41:42.333
Right?

00:41:42.966 --> 00:41:43.766
Yeah.

00:41:47.133 --> 00:41:48.000
P'Charm...

00:41:48.600 --> 00:41:49.100
Yes?

00:41:49.100 --> 00:41:50.266
Look at that girl.

00:41:55.800 --> 00:41:57.933
What do you think she's feeling right now?

00:42:04.700 --> 00:42:05.925
I think

00:42:06.162 --> 00:42:09.903
she's gathering all her courage.

00:42:18.800 --> 00:42:19.853
Excuse me.

00:42:21.935 --> 00:42:23.173
You...

00:42:23.694 --> 00:42:24.937
What's your name?

00:42:25.666 --> 00:42:27.634
Uh, I'm...

00:42:27.634 --> 00:42:29.000
My name is Prim.

00:42:30.400 --> 00:42:31.200
You...

00:42:34.366 --> 00:42:36.266
you want to give him something, right?

00:42:37.666 --> 00:42:41.328
Uh, well...

00:42:42.464 --> 00:42:43.560
Yes.

00:42:43.891 --> 00:42:47.192
But I'm afraid he won't want it.

00:42:50.100 --> 00:42:51.277
Be brave.

00:42:52.224 --> 00:42:53.479
Even if he doesn't accept it,

00:42:53.810 --> 00:42:54.929
it's okay.

00:42:55.260 --> 00:42:56.930
At least

00:42:57.545 --> 00:43:00.000
you got to do what your heart wanted.

00:43:04.933 --> 00:43:06.266
Thank you, Auntie.

00:43:14.100 --> 00:43:14.900
Auntie?

00:43:35.333 --> 00:43:36.133
That was so sweet.

00:43:58.966 --> 00:43:59.766
P'Charm...

00:44:08.566 --> 00:44:09.933
Happy Valentine's Day.

00:44:20.766 --> 00:44:21.566
So cute.

00:44:22.400 --> 00:44:23.800
Thank you, Auntie.

00:45:15.133 --> 00:45:16.533
Today feels like a dream.

00:45:17.800 --> 00:45:20.000
I never thought I'd see you again, P'Charm.

00:45:22.333 --> 00:45:23.133
For me,

00:45:25.166 --> 00:45:28.466
it's felt like a dream since the moment
you walked through that door.

00:45:32.666 --> 00:45:34.382
I never thought

00:45:34.903 --> 00:45:36.491
that my crush

00:45:38.006 --> 00:45:39.796
would be standing right in front of me.

00:45:40.166 --> 00:45:41.966
You still remember, P'Charm?

00:45:42.766 --> 00:45:43.766
I've never forgotten.

00:45:45.100 --> 00:45:46.097
Do you know?

00:45:46.571 --> 00:45:48.497
Throughout all these years,

00:45:50.379 --> 00:45:52.104
I kept asking myself

00:45:53.571 --> 00:45:55.021
how I

00:45:56.333 --> 00:45:58.100
would confess my feelings to you.

00:45:59.866 --> 00:46:00.966
And now?

00:46:02.333 --> 00:46:03.566
I miss everything about it.

00:46:22.000 --> 00:46:23.000
P'Charm...

00:46:27.133 --> 00:46:28.766
how much do you miss me?

00:46:31.933 --> 00:46:32.733
I...

00:46:35.900 --> 00:46:37.766
miss every inch of your body.

00:46:40.700 --> 00:46:41.766
Which part?

00:46:43.900 --> 00:46:46.133
This part?

00:46:49.100 --> 00:46:49.900
This part?

00:46:52.600 --> 00:46:53.700
Or maybe...

00:46:56.700 --> 00:46:57.500
this part?

00:47:03.666 --> 00:47:04.600
P'Charm...

00:47:07.466 --> 00:47:08.266
what are you doing?

00:47:11.600 --> 00:47:13.366
Let me be the one to start.

00:49:12.486 --> 00:49:13.608
Back then, as a shy nerd,
I stood with a Valentine's gift,

00:49:13.608 --> 00:49:14.778
too scared to say a word to P’Charm.

00:49:14.778 --> 00:49:16.209
Unbelievably, that was the start
of our entire journey.

00:49:16.209 --> 00:49:17.972
Through fear and pressure,
we were once driven apart.

00:49:18.020 --> 00:49:19.041
Yet in the end,
we still chose one another.

00:49:19.041 --> 00:49:19.999
I’ve learned that true love means never letting go,

00:49:20.000 --> 00:49:20.994
no matter the obstacles.

00:49:20.994 --> 00:49:21.897
I’m not that girl anymore,

00:49:21.897 --> 00:49:22.959
but no matter how many Valentines pass,
my heart still races.

00:49:22.959 --> 00:49:23.894
I love P’Charm as much as ever,
and more with each passing day.